critter.name: Darner Dragonfly
critter.desc: At first glance, the darner dragonfly, like all dragonflies, appears to be quite a sleek bug, wot? But in its larval stage, this bug is a beastly little carnivore... I suppose if one were being eaten, one wouldn't care if whoever was doing the devouring looked sleek...
critter.quote: I caught a darner dragonfly! It better watch its mouth!
